<p class="ayah 12-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ لَّقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوسُفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Yusuf</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِخْوَتِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his brothers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَـٰتٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّلسَّآئِلِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for those who ask.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>7<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
