<p class="ayah 12-41" id="41" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰصَـٰحِبَىِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O my two companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسِّجْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the prison!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">As for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَدُكُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one of you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيَسْقِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he will give drink</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) his master</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَمْرًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wine;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and as for</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَخَرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the other</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيُصْلَبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he will be crucified,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَأْكُلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and will eat</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلطَّيْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the birds</span></span><span class