<p class="ayah 12-50" id="50" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَلِكُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the king,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱئْتُونِى بِهِۦ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Bring him to me."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّسُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the messenger,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱرْجِعْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Return</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَسْــَٔلْهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and ask him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first