<p class="ayah 12-69" id="69" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَخَلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they entered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">upon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوسُفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Yusuf,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاوَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he took</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to himself</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخَاهُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his brother.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَا۟</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] am</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخُوكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your brother</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَ