<p class="ayah 12-70" id="70" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَهَّزَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he had furnished them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِجَهَازِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with their supplies,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he put</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسِّقَايَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the drinking cup</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَحْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the bag</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) his brother.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَذَّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">called out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُؤَذِّنٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an announcer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيَّتُهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"O you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar qura