<p class="ayah 12-87" id="87" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰبَنِىَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O my sons!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱذْهَبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Go</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَحَسَّسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and inquire</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوسُفَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Yusuf</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَخِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his brother,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَاْيْــَٔسُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">despair</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَّوْحِ ٱللَّهِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Mercy of Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">none</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" d