<p class="ayah 12-106" id="106" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْمِنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْثَرُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">most of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّشْرِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate partners with Him.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>106<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
