<p class="ayah 12-108" id="108" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"This</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) my way;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَدْعُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I invite</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَصِيرَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">insight,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَا۟</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّبَعَنِى‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">follows me.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَسُبْحَـٰنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Glory be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</