<p class="ayah 12-109" id="109" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرْسَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We sent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قَبْلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رِجَالاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">men</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُّوحِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from (among)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرَىٰٓ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the townships.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So have not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسِيرُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they traveled</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText