<p class="ayah 12-110" id="110" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَيْــَٔسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">gave up hope</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرُّسُلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messengers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَظَنُّوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and thought</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُذِبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were denied,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then came to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَصْرُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our help,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَنُجِّىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and was saved</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَّشَآءُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We willed.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُرَدُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(can) be repelled</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَأْسُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَوْمِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(who are) criminals.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>110<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 12-111" id="111" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Verily,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(there) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَصَصِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their stories</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبْرَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a lesson</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّأُوْلِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for men</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَلْبَـٰبِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) understanding.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(it) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَدِيثًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a narration</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُفْتَرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">invented,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَـٰكِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">